import React from 'react'
import {Container, SearchBar, CitiesMetropolis, OverseasCities,SearchTitle,SearchInput,CitiesTitle,OvereasTitle} from './CitiesElements'

const CitiesSearch = () => {
    return (
        <Container>
            <SearchBar>
                <SearchTitle>Je recherche... </SearchTitle>
                <SearchInput 
                 type="text"
                 name="search"
                 placeholder=" ...une ville, un code postal"
                />
            </SearchBar>
            <CitiesMetropolis>
                <CitiesTitle> villes de metropole</CitiesTitle>
            </CitiesMetropolis>
            <OverseasCities>
                <OvereasTitle>ville d'outre-mer</OvereasTitle>
            </OverseasCities>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default CitiesSearch
